name: RoboticsWhatShouldYouDo
skdetail:

Invocation Name: robotics trivia
des: A fun and easy trivia game designed to quiz and teach you some STEAM and robotics related things you may not have know. A question would be given out, and you will have the option of choosing one of the four possible answers to answer the question. Some of the answers may be silly, but others are quite informative.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
